  "date": "2026-02-25",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Corruption\nRisk Mapping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Interview\nSummary Report<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td width=\"141\" style=\"width:105.45pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Item</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"549\" style=\"width:411.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Information</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"141\" style=\"width:105.45pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Date\n  of interview</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"549\" style=\"width:411.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">February 25, 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"141\" style=\"width:105.45pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewee</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"549\" style=\"width:411.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Paulina <span style=\"text-transform:\n  uppercase\">Escobedo Solórzano</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"141\" style=\"width:105.45pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Position</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"549\" style=\"width:411.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Managing Director – LFB Mexico<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"141\" style=\"width:105.45pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewers</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"549\" style=\"width:411.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Antoine <span style=\"text-transform:\n  uppercase\">LassaUge</span>, Sandra LASAGNI<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">1. Responsibilities, scope and activities<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Department\n     / role:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> <b>Managing Director of LFB Mexico</b>,\n     with cross‑functional oversight of commercial operations, compliance\n     support, institutional relations, and internal controls. Significant year‑on‑year\n     growth and strong profit expectations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Geographical\n     scope:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> Entire Mexican territory, covering <b>32\n     states</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Team\n     size:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;\n     mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> <b>25 employees</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Organizational\n     context</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">:<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">LFB\n      Mexico experienced significant transitions in 2024–2025 with <b>30% new\n      hires in 2025</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No <b>local\n      compliance committee</b> currently exists, despite a recognized need.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Compliance\n      responsibilities are split between the Managing Director and CFO, who\n      also manages procurement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Key missions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Overall\n      leadership</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> of LFB Mexico and development of the\n      affiliate.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Management\n      of governmental sales </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">(~90% of revenues).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Commercial\n      operations</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">, including <b>tender participation</b>, <b>contract\n      negotiation</b>, and <b>long‑term contracting</b> (through 2027–2028).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Implementation\n      and use of SAP</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">, including modules for\n      procurement, commercial, and quality processes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Oversight\n      of distributors</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">, including mandatory legal\n      contracts, background checks, onboarding, verification of documents and\n      financials, and on-site visits where necessary.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Supplier and procurement\n      oversight</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">signature\n       of NDAs and contracts,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">review of quotations,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">informal audits of procurement\n       decisions,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">coordination\n       with procurement and legal advisors.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Internal\n      processes and controls</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">: review of expenses, travel,\n      and internal reporting,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk\n      and compliance oversight</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n      11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">, together with the local\n      compliance officer, including: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">implementation of background\n       checks,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">documentation\n       of processes, <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">conflict‑of‑interest\n       declarations,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">development of compliance\n       culture.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Representation of LFB</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> within: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">the <b>Mexican</b>\n       <b>Pharma Industry Association</b> <b>“AMIIF”</b> (as a board member),<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">interactions\n       with <b>public authorities</b> (e.g., Ministry of Health, Ministry of Economy,\n       Anti‑corruption office),<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">the\n       French Embassy (Club Santé),<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">peer companies (AstraZeneca,\n       Novartis, Sanofi, etc.).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Employee\n      security management</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> due to increasing external\n      criminal risks (drug cartel activity).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">2. Third parties, interactions, corruption risks and controls<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A.\nLocal Health Authorities (Ministry of Health, hospitals, public institutions)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Tender\n      preparation, market research requests, contract execution, payment\n      follow-up.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Occasional\n      direct phone calls from authorities imposing a specific distributor.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Frequency:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:\n     EN-US\"> Regular in tender periods; “once a year” for imposed distributor\n     cases.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Business\n     volume:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> Represents <b>90% of LFB Mexico revenues</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks identified:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Imposition\n      of distributors</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> without transparent\n      justification: risk of non‑compliant contracting if teams accept without\n      questioning.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Potential\n      political influence, especially during election periods (17 states in\n      upcoming elections).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Required\n      <b>official written requests</b> from authorities.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Asking\n      for justification of distributor assignment.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Checklist</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:\n      EN-US\"> of questions to ask before accepting.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Increased\n      <b>digital processes</b> reducing risk (anonymized tender officers,\n      traceability).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">D.\nGovernment Authorities outside the Health Sector (Ministry of Economy, Anti‑Corruption\nOffice, French Embassy)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Meetings\n      through the Pharma Association (board participation).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Collective\n      advocacy.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Institutional\n      discussions related to payments, regulations, health sector governance.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks identified:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Theoretical\n      risk of perceived or actual influence‑seeking.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Participation through formal\n      associations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Documented and transparent\n      interactions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Low\n      profile maintained voluntarily by Managing Director.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">B. Distributors<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Central\n      to LFB Mexico's operations due to reliance on distributors in <b>32\n      Mexican states</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Selection,\n      due diligence/ background checks, site visits, contract negotiation and\n      signature.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Management\n      of imposed distributors (assigned directly by local authorities with a\n      lack of justification): new distributors sometimes emerge “out of\n      nowhere” in certain states.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks identified:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Political\n      influence in distributor selection.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Pressure\n      to work with unknown distributors, sometimes unsuitable entities.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      corruption or involvement with fraudulent companies (Joint liability\n      under Mexican anticorruption law).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Conflict\n      of interest case observed:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n      11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> sister of an LFB\n      employee working for a distributor pushing for a contract.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\nmargin-left:35.7pt;text-indent:-17.85pt;page-break-after:avoid;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4;\ntab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:\nSymbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Controls mentioned:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Contracts\n      mandatory for all distributors. No business before contract is signed.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Background\n      checks prior to entering into the relationship (however current provider not\n      considered as the best). Need for periodic background checks (not yet in\n      place).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Possibility\n      to refuse the business in case the distributor is not acceptable.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Site\n      visits, reference checks for suspicious cases.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">C.\nSuppliers / External service providers (IT, consultants, legal advisors, marketing\nagencies)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Frequent\n      onboarding of new suppliers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Standard\n      process: NDA → quotation/proposal → internal evaluation and selection →\n      contract.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks identified:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      biased supplier selection due to personal links or insufficient\n      background checks (e.g., conflict of interest / favoritism).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Historical\n      cases discovered upon joining the affiliate.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Purchasing process requiring\n      2–3 quotes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Hierarchical approvals.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Four‑eyes\n      principle: supplier signs → procurement → final signature by Managing\n      Director.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Audit\n      trail in SAP (though data storage limitations exist).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Informal quarterly expense\n      reviews.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">E.\nInternal Risks (confidentiality, HR, compliance governance)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Key concerns:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No\n      compliance committee yet (considered “a must” for 2026).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Insufficient\n      maturity of middle management regarding compliance expectations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">High\n      turnover increases risk of confidentiality breaches and impact on\n      internal culture.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Insufficient\n      structure around sensitive data classification and access.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Conflict‑of‑interest\n      policy exists but is not updated annually.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Plans\n      for structured training (managers first, then employees).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Coaching\n      program for middle management to strengthen compliance culture.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Contract\n      filing practices being reinforced with Legal.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>",
